<LP>
   ImmunoGen Inc. said it signed an agreement with Takeda
Chemical Industries Ltd. of Japan that will enable ImmunoGen
to develop Takeda's maytansine experimental anti-cancer drug.
   Under the agreement, the Cambridge, Mass.-based
biotechnology concern has an option to exclusively license
